WITH A AS (SELECT DISTINCT S.PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') SELECT DISTINCT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND S.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT * FROM A)

WITH CTE AS (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE (SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') AND PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE <'2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE> '2019-03-31')) SELECT C.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM CTE C JOIN PRODUCT P ON C.PRODUCT_ID=P.PRODUCT_ID

WITH NT1 AS ( SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME, SALES.SALE_DATE FROM SALES LEFT JOIN PRODUCT ON SALES.PRODUCT_ID = PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID ) SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM NT1 GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(NT1.SALE_DATE)>='2019-01-01' AND MAX(NT1.SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

WITH SOLD_OTHER AS (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' ) SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SOLD_OTHER)

WITH T1 AS ( SELECT P.PRODUCT_NAME, P.PRODUCT_ID, S.SALE_DATE, CASE WHEN S.SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS TEMP1 FROM PRODUCT P INNER JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID ) SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM T1 WHERE TEMP1 = 1 AND PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM T1 WHERE TEMP1 = 0)

WITH A AS( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, (CASE WHEN SALE_DATE>='2019-01-01' AND SALE_DATE<='2019-03-31' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS SPRING_SALE FROM SALES), B AS ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, SUM(SPRING_SALE) AS SPRING_SALE, COUNT(*) AS TOTAL FROM A GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING SPRING_SALE != 0 AND TOTAL = SPRING_SALE) SELECT B.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME FROM B JOIN PRODUCT ON B.PRODUCT_ID = PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID

WITH ALL_PRODUCTS_Q_2_3_4 AS ( SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES S INNER JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE QUARTER(S.SALE_DATE) != '1' ) SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT * FROM ALL_PRODUCTS_Q_2_3_4)

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') ) SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM CTE)

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, SUM(QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_SOLD, SUM(CASE WHEN SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' THEN QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS SOLD_SPRING FROM SALES GROUP BY 1 ) SELECT C.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM CTE C JOIN PRODUCT P ON C.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE TOTAL_SOLD = SOLD_SPRING

WITH JANMAR AS ( SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' ), NONJANMAR AS ( SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' ), IDLIST AS ( SELECT I.PRODUCT_ID FROM JANMAR I LEFT OUTER JOIN NONJANMAR N ON I.PRODUCT_ID = N.PRODUCT_ID WHERE N.PRODUCT_ID IS NULL ) SELECT I.PRODUCT_ID, N.PRODUCT_NAME FROM IDLIST I LEFT OUTER JOIN PRODUCT N ON I.PRODUCT_ID = N.PRODUCT_ID

WITH MAIN AS ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME, (CASE WHEN SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS DATES, (CASE WHEN SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS NON_DATES FROM SALES INNER JOIN PRODUCT USING(PRODUCT_ID) ) SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM MAIN GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING SUM(DATES) > 0 AND SUM(NON_DATES) = 0

WITH MIN_MAX AS (SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME, MIN(SALE_DATE) AS MIN_SALE, MAX(SALE_DATE) AS MAX_SALE FROM SALES S INNER JOIN PRODUCT P ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY 1) SELECT MM.PRODUCT_ID, MM.PRODUCT_NAME FROM MIN_MAX MM WHERE MM.MIN_SALE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND MM.MAX_SALE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31'

WITH OTHER_THAN_2019_SPRING AS ( SELECT DISTINCT(PRODUCT_ID) FROM SALES AS S WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' ) SELECT DISTINCT(S.PRODUCT_ID), P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES AS S JOIN PRODUCT AS P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE >= '2019-01-01' AND SALE_DATE < '2019-04-01' AND S.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT * FROM OTHER_THAN_2019_SPRING)

WITH SOLD_PRODUCTS AS ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31' ) SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SOLD_PRODUCTS S INNER JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID

WITH SOLD_SPRING AS (SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31'), SOLD_OTHER AS (SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') SELECT DISTINCT SP.PRODUCT_ID, SP.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SOLD_SPRING SP WHERE SP.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SOLD_OTHER)

WITH SPRING AS ( SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' ), NON_SPRING AS ( SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE (DATE(S.SALE_DATE) < DATE('2019-01-01') OR DATE(S.SALE_DATE) > DATE('2019-03-31')) ) SELECT DISTINCT SPRING.PRODUCT_ID, SPRING.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SPRING WHERE SPRING.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT NON_SPRING.PRODUCT_ID FROM NON_SPRING)

WITH SPRING AS (SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES AS S JOIN PRODUCT AS P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31'), NOT_SPRING AS ( SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES AS S JOIN PRODUCT AS P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') SELECT DISTINCT SPRING.PRODUCT_ID, SPRING.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SPRING WHERE SPRING.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM NOT_SPRING)

WITH T1 AS (SELECT DISTINCT(PRODUCT_ID) PID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31'), T2 AS (SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME, S.SALE_DATE FROM SALES S JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID) SELECT DISTINCT(PRODUCT_ID), PRODUCT_NAME FROM T2 WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PID FROM T1)

WITH T1 AS (SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN S.SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS SPRING_SALE, SUM(CASE WHEN S.SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR S.SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS OUTSIDE_SPRING_SALE FROM SALES S JOIN PRODUCT P USING(PRODUCT_ID) GROUP BY 1,2) SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM T1 WHERE SPRING_SALE > 0 AND OUTSIDE_SPRING_SALE = 0

WITH CTE1 AS (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S USING(PRODUCT_ID) WHERE S.SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT * FROM CTE1)

WITH TB AS ( SELECT S.*, P.PRODUCT_NAME, P.UNIT_PRICE FROM SALES S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID) SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM TB WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM TB WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE >'2019-03-31' )

WITH TB AS ( SELECT S.*, P.PRODUCT_NAME, P.UNIT_PRICE FROM SALES S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID) SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM TB WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM TB WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE >'2019-03-31' )
SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID, A.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT A LEFT JOIN SALES B ON A.PRODUCT_ID = B.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY A.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(B.SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31' AND MIN(B.SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01'

SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID=P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(S.SALE_DATE)>= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(S.SALE_DATE)<='2019-03-31'
SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY 1,2 HAVING MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31' AND MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01'

SELECT S1.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE >'2019-03-31') ) S1 LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON S1.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID
SELECT SALES.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES JOIN PRODUCT ON SALES.PRODUCT_ID = PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

SELECT T1.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') T1 JOIN PRODUCT T2 ON T1.PRODUCT_ID = T2.PRODUCT_ID

WITH CTE AS(SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID, A.PRODUCT_NAME, B.SALE_DATE,B.QUANTITY FROM PRODUCT A LEFT JOIN SALES B ON A.PRODUCT_ID = B.PRODUCT_ID ) SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME, SUM(CASE WHEN SALE_DATE>=DATE('2019-01-01') AND SALE_DATE<=('2019-03-31') THEN QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) SPRING_19_SALES, SUM(CASE WHEN SALE_DATE<DATE('2019-01-01') OR SALE_DATE>('2019-03-31') THEN QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) OTHER_SALES FROM CTE GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID) C WHERE SPRING_19_SALES > 0 AND OTHER_SALES = 0

WITH A AS( SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME, CASE WHEN SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31 THEN Y ELSE N' END AS Q1_SALE FROM SALES JOIN PRODUCT ON SALES.PRODUCT_ID=PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID) SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM A GROUP BY 1,2 HAVING MIN(Q1_SALE)='Y'

WITH C1 AS (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31')) SELECT C1.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM C1 LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P USING(PRODUCT_ID)

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID,P.PRODUCT_NAME,MIN(S.SALE_DATE) OVER(PARTITION BY PRODUCT_ID) AS MINIMUM , MAX(S.SALE_DATE) OVER(PARTITION BY PRODUCT_ID) AS MAXIMUM FROM SALES S INNER JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID ) SELECT PRODUCT_ID,PRODUCT_NAME FROM CTE WHERE MINIMUM >= '2019-01-01' AND MAXIMUM <= '2019-03-31' GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR S.SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' ) SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM CTE)

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' ) SELECT * FROM CTE WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE MONTH(SALE_DATE) > 3)

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' ), TEMP AS ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' ), SUB AS ( SELECT CTE.PRODUCT_ID FROM CTE LEFT JOIN TEMP ON CTE.PRODUCT_ID=TEMP.PRODUCT_ID WHERE TEMP.PRODUCT_ID IS NULL ) SELECT DISTINCT SUB.PRODUCT_ID,P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SUB JOIN PRODUCT AS P ON SUB.PRODUCT_ID=P.PRODUCT_ID ORDER BY SUB.PRODUCT_ID
WITH CTE AS ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM CTE)

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE<'2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE>'2019-03-31' ), DEMO AS ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE>='2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE<='2019-03-31' ), SUB AS ( SELECT DEMO.PRODUCT_ID FROM DEMO LEFT JOIN CTE ON DEMO.PRODUCT_ID=CTE.PRODUCT_ID WHERE CTE.PRODUCT_ID IS NULL ) SELECT DISTINCT SUB.PRODUCT_ID,P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SUB JOIN PRODUCT AS P ON SUB.PRODUCT_ID=P.PRODUCT_ID ORDER BY PRODUCT_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID, A.SALE_DATE, B.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES A JOIN PRODUCT B ON A.PRODUCT_ID = B.PRODUCT_ID) SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM CTE WHERE PRODUCT_ID IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM CTE WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') AND PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM CTE WHERE (SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01') OR (SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31')) GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME

WITH CTE AS (SELECT PRODUCT_ID , SUM(CASE WHEN SALE_DATE>='2019-01-01' AND SALE_DATE<='2019-03-31' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS SPRING , SUM(CASE WHEN SALE_DATE<'2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE>'2019-03-31' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS OTHER FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID ) SELECT CTE. PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM CTE, PRODUCT WHERE CTE. PRODUCT_ID=PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID AND SPRING>=1 AND OTHER=0

WITH JOINTABLE AS (SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID, B.PRODUCT_NAME, A.SALE_DATE FROM SALES AS A INNER JOIN PRODUCT AS B ON A.PRODUCT_ID=B.PRODUCT_ID ) SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM JOINTABLE WHERE (PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM JOINTABLE WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31')) AND (SALE_DATE >= '2019-01-01') AND (SALE_DATE <= '2019-03-31')

WITH P AS ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES USING(PRODUCT_ID) WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' ) SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM P)
WITH PRO AS (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE<'2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE>'2019-03-31') SELECT PRODUCT_ID,PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM PRO)

WITH PRODUCT AS( SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME, SALE_DATE FROM SALES AS S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT AS P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID) SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID , PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT AS P WHERE PRODUCT_ID IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCT WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') AND PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCT WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31')

WITH PRODUCT_SOLD_SPRING AS( SELECT PRODUCT_ID,MIN(SALE_DATE) AS START_DATE,MAX(SALE_DATE) AS END_DATE FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID) SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID,P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT_SOLD_SPRING S JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID=P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE START_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND END_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31'

WITH PRODUCTS_SOLD_ON_PERIOD AS ( SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' ), PRODUCTS_NOT_SOLD_ON_PERIOD AS ( SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' ) SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCTS_NOT_SOLD_ON_PERIOD) AND PRODUCT_ID IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCTS_SOLD_ON_PERIOD)

WITH RESULT AS (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM RESULT)

WITH S1 AS (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES INNER JOIN PRODUCT ON SALES.PRODUCT_ID = PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE >= '2019-01-01' AND SALE_DATE <= '2019-03-31') SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM S1 WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES INNER JOIN PRODUCT ON SALES.PRODUCT_ID = PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31')

WITH SALES_CTE AS( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' GROUP BY SELLER_ID,PRODUCT_ID,BUYER_ID,SALE_DATE ) SELECT PRODUCT_ID,PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT * FROM SALES_CTE )

WITH SALES_CTE AS( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' GROUP BY SELLER_ID,PRODUCT_ID,BUYER_ID,SALE_DATE,QUANTITY ) SELECT PRODUCT_ID,PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT * FROM SALES_CTE )

WITH SALES_LIST AS (SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID,S.SALE_DATE,P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID =P.PRODUCT_ID) SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID,PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES_LIST WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES_LIST WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31')

WITH SALESINFO AS (SELECT PRODUCT_ID , SUM(CASE WHEN SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS FLAG FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID) SELECT PRODUCT_ID , PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALESINFO WHERE FLAG = 0)

WITH SOLD AS ( SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' ), NOT_SOLD AS ( SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' ) SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM NOT_SOLD) AND PRODUCT_ID IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SOLD)

WITH SPRING AS (SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31'), NOT_SPRING AS (SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') SELECT DISTINCT(SP.PRODUCT_ID), SP.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SPRING AS SP WHERE SP.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM NOT_SPRING)

WITH SPRINGIN AS ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' ), SPRINGOUT AS ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE<'2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE>'2019-03-31' ) SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SPRINGIN) AND PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SPRINGOUT)

WITH T(PRODUCT_ID) AS ( SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCT P INNER JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID=S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE<'2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE>'2019-03-31' ) SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID,P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P INNER JOIN SALES S ON S.PRODUCT_ID=P.PRODUCT_ID LEFT JOIN T ON T.PRODUCT_ID=S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND T.PRODUCT_ID IS NULL

WITH T1 AS ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM T1)

WITH T1 AS (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT AS P WHERE P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM T1)

WITH TAB AS ( SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME, S.SALE_DATE FROM PRODUCT AS P JOIN SALES AS S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID ) SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM TAB GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

WITH TEMP AS (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE< '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31') SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE>= '2019-01-01' AND SALE_DATE <= '2019-03-31' AND P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT *FROM TEMP) ORDER BY 1

WITH TEMP AS (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' )) SELECT DISTINCT TEMP.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM TEMP JOIN PRODUCT PRO ON PRO.PRODUCT_ID=TEMP.PRODUCT_ID

WITH TEMP AS( SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME, SALE_DATE FROM PRODUCT P RIGHT JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID =S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' ) SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM TEMP WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID

WITH TEMP(PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME) AS (SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID, A.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT A INNER JOIN SALES B ON A.PRODUCT_ID=B.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE <'2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE>'2019-03-31') SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID, A.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT A INNER JOIN SALES B ON A.PRODUCT_ID=B.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY A.PRODUCT_ID HAVING A.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM TEMP)

WITH TMP AS (SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME, SALE_DATE FROM SALES A JOIN PRODUCT B ON A.PRODUCT_ID = B.PRODUCT_ID) SELECT DISTINCT A.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM TMP A WHERE A.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM TMP WHERE SALE_DATE < DATE('2019-01-01') OR SALE_DATE > DATE('2019-03-31'))

WITH TMP AS (SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') SELECT PRODUCT_ID,PRODUCT_NAME FROM TMP WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID AS PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE DATEDIFF(SALE_DATE,'2019-01-01')<0 OR DATEDIFF(SALE_DATE,'2019-03-31')>0)

WITH TMP AS (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, MAX(SALE_DATE) MAXDATE, MIN(SALE_DATE) MINDATE FROM SALES GROUP BY 1) SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID, B.PRODUCT_NAME FROM TMP A INNER JOIN PRODUCT B ON A.PRODUCT_ID = B.PRODUCT_ID WHERE A.MAXDATE <= '2019-03-31' AND A.MINDATE >= '2019-01-01'

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT INNER JOIN SALES ON PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID = SALES.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALES.SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' ) SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT CTE.PRODUCT_ID FROM CTE )

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P INNER JOIN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES GROUP BY 1 HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31' ) S ON (P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID)
SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES JOIN PRODUCT USING (PRODUCT_ID) WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' )

SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID, A.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT A, (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, MIN(SALE_DATE) AS MIN_DATE, MAX(SALE_DATE) AS MAX_DATE FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID) B WHERE A.PRODUCT_ID=B.PRODUCT_ID AND B.MIN_DATE >= '2019-01-01' AND B.MAX_DATE <= '2019-03-31'
SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31' AND MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' )
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID,P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

SELECT DISTINCT B.PRODUCT_ID, A.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT AS A JOIN SALES AS B ON A.PRODUCT_ID = B.PRODUCT_ID WHERE B.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' OR SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' )
SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01 00:00:00' AND '2019-03-31 23:59:59' )
SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' )
SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING SUM(SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31') = 0

SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID,PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID IN (SELECT SALES.PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES GROUP BY SALES.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(SALE_DATE)<='2019-03-31' AND MIN(SALE_DATE)>='2019-01-01' )
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P LEFT JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID=S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(S.SALE_DATE)>= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(S.SALE_DATE)<='2019-03-31'
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN(SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31')

SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31')

SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(S.SALE_DATE) >= CAST('2019-01-01' AS DATE) AND MAX(S.SALE_DATE) <= CAST('2019-03-31' AS DATE)
SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID IN( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING '2019-01-01'<= MIN(SALE_DATE) AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <='2019-03-31' )

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID IN (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') AND PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31')

SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= CAST('2019-01-01' AS DATE) AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= CAST('2019-03-31' AS DATE)

SELECT DISTINCT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT S.PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES S WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31')

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P INNER JOIN SALES S ON (P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID) GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID HAVING (MIN(S.SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(S.SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31')

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P LEFT JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID HAVING SUM(S.SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') = COUNT(S.SALE_DATE)

SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31')
SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID <> ALL ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE DATE(SALE_DATE) NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31')

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P INNER JOIN SALES S USING(PRODUCT_ID) GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= CAST('2019-01-01' AS DATE) AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= CAST('2019-03-31' AS DATE)

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT AS P WHERE P.PRODUCT_ID IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES AS S GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(S.SALE_DATE) BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-04-01' AND MIN(S.SALE_DATE) BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-04-01')
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES AS S INNER JOIN PRODUCT AS P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY 1,2 HAVING MIN(S.SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(S.SALE_DATE ) <= '2019-03-31'

WITH PRODUCT_DATES AS ( SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME, MIN(S.SALE_DATE) AS FIRST_DATE, MAX(S.SALE_DATE) AS LAST_DATE FROM PRODUCT AS P JOIN SALES AS S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID ) SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT_DATES WHERE FIRST_DATE >= '2019-01-01' AND FIRST_DATE <= '2019-03-31' AND LAST_DATE >= '2019-01-01' AND LAST_DATE <= '2019-03-31'

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM ( SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME, S.SALE_DATE FROM PRODUCT P LEFT JOIN SALES S ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING YEAR(S.SALE_DATE) = 2019 AND MONTH(S.SALE_DATE) < 4 ) T
SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) < '2019-04-01')

SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID, A.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT A INNER JOIN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, MAX(SALE_DATE) AS A1, MIN(SALE_DATE) AS A2 FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID) AS TEMP ON TEMP.PRODUCT_ID = A.PRODUCT_ID WHERE TEMP.A1<='2019-03-31' AND TEMP.A2>='2019-01-01'

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P LEFT JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING S.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN'2019-01-01'AND'2019-03-31')
SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S INNER JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S INNER JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID HAVING SUM(CASE WHEN SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' THEN 0 ELSE 1 END) = 0

WITH TMP AS ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, MIN(SALE_DATE) AS MIN_DATE, MAX(SALE_DATE) AS MAX_DATE FROM SALES GROUP BY 1) SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID, B.PRODUCT_NAME FROM TMP A LEFT JOIN PRODUCT B ON A.PRODUCT_ID = B.PRODUCT_ID WHERE A.MIN_DATE >= DATE('2019-01-01') AND A.MAX_DATE <= DATE('2019-03-31')
SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT S1.PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES S1 WHERE S1.SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR S1.SALE_DATE >'2019-03-31' )

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE >= '2019-01-01' AND SALE_DATE <= '2019-03-31' ) AND PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' )
SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT JOIN SALES USING(PRODUCT_ID) GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING '2019-01-01' <= MIN(SALE_DATE) AND MAX(SALE_DATE) < '2019-04-01'
SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE DATE(SALE_DATE) NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31')
SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE > CAST('2019-03-31' AS DATE) OR SALE_DATE < CAST('2019-01-01' AS DATE) )
SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES S WHERE SALE_DATE > CAST('2019-03-31' AS DATE) OR SALE_DATE < CAST('2019-01-01' AS DATE) )

WITH CTE AS (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31'), CTE1 AS (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31') SELECT PRODUCT_ID,PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID IN (SELECT * FROM CTE) AND PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT * FROM CTE1)

SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES JOIN PRODUCT ON SALES.PRODUCT_ID = PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY SALES.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31'
SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID, A.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT A WHERE A.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT C.PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES C WHERE C.SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' OR C.SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' )

SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S JOIN PRODUCT P WHERE S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID AND P.PRODUCT_ID IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' ) AND P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' )
SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE MONTH(SALE_DATE)>3)

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID

WITH NON_SPRING AS ( SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' ) SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM NON_SPRING )
SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID , PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT INNER JOIN SALES ON PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID=SALES.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(QUARTER(SALES.SALE_DATE))=1
SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID , PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT JOIN SALES ON PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID = SALES.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(QUARTER(SALE_DATE)) = 1

SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P INNER JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND NOT EXISTS ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID AND (SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31') )

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES GROUP BY 1 HAVING COUNT(CASE WHEN SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' THEN PRODUCT_ID END) = COUNT(PRODUCT_ID))

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME HAVING SUM(SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31')>0 AND SUM(SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31')=0

SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID,P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME HAVING (MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01') AND (MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31')

SELECT DISTINCT SL.PRODUCT_ID PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES SL JOIN PRODUCT PROD ON SL.PRODUCT_ID = PROD.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID,P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P WHERE P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN( SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID=S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE NOT S.SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' )

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' ) AND PRODUCT_ID IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE >= '2019-01-01' AND SALE_DATE <= '2019-03-31' )

SELECT PRODUCT_ID,PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES NATURAL JOIN PRODUCT WHERE SALE_DATE<'2019-03-31' AND SALE_DATE>'2019-01-01' AND PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE>'2019-03-31' OR SALE_DATE<'2019-01-01') GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P LEFT JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(QUARTER(SALE_DATE)) = 1

WITH SALES_NOT_1Q_2022 AS ( SELECT S.* FROM SALES S WHERE S.SALE_DATE <'2019-01-01' OR S.SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' ) SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P WHERE P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES_NOT_1Q_2022)
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID,PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P WHERE P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' OR SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' )
SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID,P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID=S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(S.SALE_DATE)>='2019-01-01' AND MAX(S.SALE_DATE)<='2019-03-31'

SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID AS PRODUCT_ID,(SELECT PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID=S.PRODUCT_ID) AS PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(S.SALE_DATE )<='2019-03-31' AND MIN(S.SALE_DATE)>='2019-01-01'

SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES LEFT JOIN PRODUCT ON PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID = SALES.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY SALES.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(SALES.SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31' AND MIN(SALES.SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01'
SELECT PRODUCT_ID, MAX(PRODUCT_NAME) PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES LEFT JOIN PRODUCT USING(PRODUCT_ID) GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(QUARTER(SALE_DATE)) = 1
SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31')

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P WHERE EXISTS ( SELECT 1 FROM SALES A WHERE A.SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-1-1' AND '2019-03-31' AND A.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID ) AND NOT EXISTS ( SELECT 1 FROM SALES B WHERE (B.SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' OR B.SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01') AND B.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID )

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT AS P LEFT JOIN SALES AS S ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(S.SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31' AND MIN(S.SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01'

SELECT DISTINCT(P.PRODUCT_ID), P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P LEFT JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE >= '2019-01-01' AND S.SALE_DATE <= '2019-03-31' AND P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCT P LEFT JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR S.SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31')
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT AS P JOIN SALES AS S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(QUARTER(SALE_DATE)) = 1

SELECT SALES.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES LEFT JOIN PRODUCT ON SALES.PRODUCT_ID = PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY SALES.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= CAST('2019-01-01' AS DATE) AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= CAST('2019-03-31' AS DATE)
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID ,P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P LEFT JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY 1,2 HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= DATE ('2019-01-01') AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= DATE('2019-03-31')
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(S.SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(S.SALE_DATE) <='2019-03-31'
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT AS P, SALES AS S WHERE P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(S.SALE_DATE)>='2019-01-01' AND MAX(S.SALE_DATE)<='2019-03-31'
SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT JOIN SALES USING(PRODUCT_ID) GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

WITH FIRST_QUARTER_ONLY AS ( SELECT SALES.PRODUCT_ID AS PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES GROUP BY SALES.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALES.SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALES.SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31' ) SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID AS PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME AS PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID IN (SELECT * FROM FIRST_QUARTER_ONLY)

SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID,A.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT AS A LEFT JOIN SALES AS B ON A.PRODUCT_ID = B.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY B.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(B.SALE_DATE) >='2019-01-01' AND MAX(B.SALE_DATE) <='2019-03-31'

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(S.SALE_DATE) BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND MIN(S.SALE_DATE) BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31'

WITH SALES_WITHIN_TIMEFRAME AS ( SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' ), SALES_OUTSIDE_TIMEFRAME AS ( SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' ) SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES_WITHIN_TIMEFRAME S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN(SELECT * FROM SALES_OUTSIDE_TIMEFRAME)

SELECT SALES.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES, PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID = SALES.PRODUCT_ID AND SALES.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' OR SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01') GROUP BY SALES.PRODUCT_ID

SELECT T1.PRODUCT_ID, T1.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT T1 INNER JOIN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, MAX(SALE_DATE) D1, MIN(SALE_DATE) D2 FROM SALES GROUP BY 1 ) T2 ON T1.PRODUCT_ID = T2.PRODUCT_ID WHERE T2.D2 >= '2019-01-01' AND T2.D1 <= '2019-03-31'

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P INNER JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

SELECT DISTINCT TEMP_1.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, MAX(SALE_DATE) AS LD, MIN(SALE_DATE) AS FD FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING LD BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND FD BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') AS TEMP_1 LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON TEMP_1.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID

WITH TARGETPRODUCTS AS (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31' AND MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01') SELECT TARGETPRODUCTS.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM TARGETPRODUCTS INNER JOIN PRODUCT ON TARGETPRODUCTS.PRODUCT_ID = PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID
SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES A JOIN PRODUCT B USING(PRODUCT_ID) GROUP BY A.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P INNER JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT AS P WHERE P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES AS S WHERE S.SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' || S.SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' )

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALES.SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' )
SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID, A.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT A JOIN SALES B ON A.PRODUCT_ID=B.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY B.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID AS PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S INNER JOIN PRODUCT P USING (PRODUCT_ID) GROUP BY 1 HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY 1,2 HAVING MIN(S.SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(S.SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID , P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P LEFT OUTER JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(S.SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(S.SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY 1 HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(QUARTER(SALE_DATE)) = 1

WITH T AS ( SELECT SALES_DATA.PRODUCT_ID, SUM(SALE_OUT) DONT_INCL FROM (SELECT *, (S.SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31') OR (S.SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01') SALE_OUT FROM SALES S) SALES_DATA GROUP BY SALES_DATA.PRODUCT_ID ) SELECT T.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM T LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON T.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE T.DONT_INCL = 0
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P WHERE P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN( SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES S WHERE S.SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' )

WITH CTE AS(SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID, A.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT A JOIN SALES B ON A.PRODUCT_ID =B.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE >= '2019-01-01' AND SALE_DATE <= '2019-03-31'), CTE1 AS(SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID, A.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT A JOIN SALES B ON A.PRODUCT_ID =B.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31') SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM CTE WHERE CTE.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM CTE1 ) ORDER BY CTE.PRODUCT_ID

SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID, B.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES A JOIN PRODUCT B ON A.PRODUCT_ID = B.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY A.PRODUCT_ID, B.PRODUCT_NAME HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'
SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES S WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31')
SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID)

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P LEFT JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(S.SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(S.SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(S.SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(S.SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P WHERE PRODUCT_ID IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31')

WITH SALESDATA AS ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, MIN(SALE_DATE) AS MINDATE, MAX(SALE_DATE) AS MAXDATE FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID ) SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID, B.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALESDATA AS A LEFT JOIN PRODUCT AS B ON A.PRODUCT_ID = B.PRODUCT_ID WHERE (MINDATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') AND (MAXDATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31')
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P INNER JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(S.SALE_DATE)<='2019-03-31' AND MIN(S.SALE_DATE)>='2019-01-01'
SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, SALE_DATE FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31' ) SELECT CTE.PRODUCT_ID AS PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME AS PRODUCT_NAME FROM CTE LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON CTE.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES S WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' )

SELECT DISTINCT(P.PRODUCT_ID),P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE P.PRODUCT_ID IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE >= '2019-01-01' AND SALE_DATE <= '2019-03-31') AND P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' OR SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01')

SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P NATURAL JOIN SALES S WHERE P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31')

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT SALES.PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCT JOIN SALES ON PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID = SALES.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' OR SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' )
SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT NATURAL JOIN SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P INNER JOIN SALES S ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT P1.PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCT P1 INNER JOIN SALES S1 ON S1.PRODUCT_ID = P1.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S1.SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31')

SELECT X.PRODUCT_ID,PRODUCT_NAME FROM ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID,MIN(SALE_DATE) AS SD,MAX(SALE_DATE) AS ED FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING SD BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND ED BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' )X LEFT JOIN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID,PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID,PRODUCT_NAME)Y ON X.PRODUCT_ID=Y.PRODUCT_ID

WITH TA1 AS( SELECT T1.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME FROM ( SELECT S1.PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES S1 WHERE S1.SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') T1 JOIN PRODUCT ON PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID = T1.PRODUCT_ID ), TA2 AS( SELECT T2.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME FROM ( SELECT S2.PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES S2 WHERE S2.SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR S2.SALE_DATE>'2019-03-31') T2 JOIN PRODUCT ON PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID = T2.PRODUCT_ID ) SELECT DISTINCT TA1.PRODUCT_ID, TA1.PRODUCT_NAME FROM TA1 WHERE (TA1.PRODUCT_ID) NOT IN (SELECT TA2.PRODUCT_ID FROM TA2)

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(S.SALE_DATE) BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND MAX(S.SALE_DATE) BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31'

WITH PRODUCTS_IN_FIRST (PRODUCT_ID, IS_IN_FIRST) AS ( SELECT DISTINCT SALES.PRODUCT_ID, TRUE AS IS_IN_FIRST FROM SALES LEFT JOIN PRODUCT ON SALES.PRODUCT_ID = PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALES.SALE_DATE >= DATE('2019-01-01') AND SALES.SALE_DATE <= DATE('2019-03-31') ), PRODUCTS_IN_REST (PRODUCT_ID, IS_IN_REST) AS ( SELECT DISTINCT SALES.PRODUCT_ID, TRUE AS IS_IN_REST FROM SALES LEFT JOIN PRODUCT ON SALES.PRODUCT_ID = PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALES.SALE_DATE > DATE('2019-03-31') OR SALES.SALE_DATE < DATE('2019-01-01') ) SELECT DISTINCT SALES.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES LEFT JOIN PRODUCT ON SALES.PRODUCT_ID = PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID LEFT JOIN PRODUCTS_IN_FIRST ON SALES.PRODUCT_ID = PRODUCTS_IN_FIRST.PRODUCT_ID LEFT JOIN PRODUCTS_IN_REST ON SALES.PRODUCT_ID = PRODUCTS_IN_REST.PRODUCT_ID WHERE PRODUCTS_IN_FIRST.IS_IN_FIRST IS TRUE AND PRODUCTS_IN_REST.IS_IN_REST IS NOT TRUE

SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCT JOIN SALES ON PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID = SALES.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' OR SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01')
SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES A LEFT JOIN PRODUCT B ON A.PRODUCT_ID = B.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY A.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE)>= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE)<='2019-03-31'

SELECT DISTINCT A.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT A INNER JOIN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE LEFT(SALE_DATE,7) BETWEEN '2019-01' AND '2019-03' AND PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE LEFT(SALE_DATE,7) NOT BETWEEN '2019-01' AND '2019-03')) B ON A.PRODUCT_ID=B.PRODUCT_ID ORDER BY 1

SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31')

SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID,PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCT JOIN SALES ON PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID=SALES.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN DATE ('2019-01-01') AND DATE ('2019-03-31'))

WITH TABLE_FINAL AS( SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME, SALE_DATE FROM SALES A LEFT JOIN PRODUCT B ON A.PRODUCT_ID=B.PRODUCT_ID) SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM TABLE_FINAL WHERE PRODUCT_ID IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM TABLE_FINAL WHERE '2019-01-01'<=SALE_DATE<='2019-03-31') AND PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM TABLE_FINAL WHERE SALE_DATE<'2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE >'2019-03-31')

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCT AS A JOIN SALES AS B ON A.PRODUCT_ID = B.PRODUCT_ID WHERE B.SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR B.SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31')
SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE YEAR(SALE_DATE)<>2019 OR MONTH(SALE_DATE)>3 )

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID AS PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCT RIGHT JOIN SALES ON PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID = SALES.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' GROUP BY PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID )
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID , P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT AS P JOIN SALES AS S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(QUARTER(S.SALE_DATE)) = 1

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES JOIN PRODUCT USING(PRODUCT_ID)) SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM CTE WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31')

SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID,PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT RIGHT JOIN SALES ON PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID=SALES.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE)>='2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE)<='2019-03-31'

SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID=P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY 1,2 HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE)>='2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE)<='2019-03-31' ORDER BY 1

SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT JOIN SALES ON PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID = SALES.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= DATE('2019-01-01') AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= DATE('2019-03-31')

SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P LEFT JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(S.SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31' AND MIN(S.SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01'

SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME FROM ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, SUM(SALE_DATE >= '2019-01-01' AND SALE_DATE <= '2019-03-31') AS SPRING_CNT, COUNT(*) AS TOTAL_CNT FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID ) AS T WHERE (SPRING_CNT >= 1) AND (TOTAL_CNT-SPRING_CNT = 0) ) AS L LEFT JOIN PRODUCT ON PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID = L.PRODUCT_ID

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, SUM(FLAG) FROM (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, SALE_DATE, CASE WHEN SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' THEN 1 WHEN SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS FLAG FROM SALES) X GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING SUM(FLAG) = 0) Y ON P.PRODUCT_ID = Y.PRODUCT_ID
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P, SALES S WHERE P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(S.SALE_DATE)<='2019-03-31' AND MIN(S.SALE_DATE)>='2019-01-01'

SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCT AS P LEFT JOIN SALES AS S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' )

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P,(SELECT PRODUCT_ID,MAX(SALE_DATE) AS MAX_SALE_DATE,MIN(SALE_DATE) AS MIN_SALE_DATE FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID) S WHERE S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID AND S.MIN_SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND S.MAX_SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31'

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31')

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT AS P LEFT JOIN SALES AS S ON P.PRODUCT_ID=S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID HAVING SUM(S.SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31')=COUNT(S.SALE_DATE)

SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT LEFT JOIN SALES ON PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID = SALES.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= CAST('2019-01-01' AS DATE) AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= CAST('2019-03-31' AS DATE)
SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S JOIN PRODUCT P USING(PRODUCT_ID) GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >='2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE)<='2019-03-31'
SELECT PRODUCT_ID , PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT CASE WHEN SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' THEN PRODUCT_ID ELSE 0 END NEW FROM SALES)

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM (SELECT PRODUCT_NAME, SALES.PRODUCT_ID AS PRODUCT_ID, SALE_DATE FROM SALES LEFT JOIN PRODUCT ON SALES.PRODUCT_ID = PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID) AS T GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING SUM(SALE_DATE <= '2019-03-31' AND SALE_DATE >= '2019-01-01') > 0 AND SUM(SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31') = 0 AND SUM(SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01') = 0
SELECT PRODUCT_ID, MAX(PRODUCT_NAME) PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES FULL JOIN PRODUCT USING(PRODUCT_ID) GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(QUARTER(SALE_DATE)) = 1

SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' ORDER BY 1 )
SELECT DISTINCT S.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

SELECT DISTINCT B.PRODUCT_ID, B.PRODUCT_NAME FROM ( SELECT * FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' ) A INNER JOIN PRODUCT B ON A.PRODUCT_ID = B.PRODUCT_ID WHERE B.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' )
SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S INNER JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(S.SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(S.SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT DISTINCT S.PRODUCT_ID,PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P INNER JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID AND S.SALE_DATE >= '2019-01-01' AND S.SALE_DATE<='2019-03-31' ) SELECT C.PRODUCT_ID,PRODUCT_NAME FROM CTE C LEFT JOIN ( SELECT SALES.PRODUCT_ID AS PD FROM SALES WHERE SALES.SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALES.SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' ) AS DT ON C.PRODUCT_ID = DT.PD WHERE DT.PD IS NULL

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT AS P INNER JOIN SALES AS S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(S.SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(S.SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID,P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P LEFT JOIN SALES S USING (PRODUCT_ID) GROUP BY 1 HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P LEFT JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID=S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE)>='2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE)<='2019-03-31'

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE >= DATE('2019-01-01') AND SALE_DATE <= DATE('2019-03-31')) AND PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE < DATE('2019-01-01') OR SALE_DATE > DATE('2019-03-31'))

SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT LEFT JOIN SALES ON PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID = SALES.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY SALES.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID,PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(QUARTER(SALE_DATE))=1

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE >= '2019-01-01' AND SALE_DATE <= '2019-03-31' ) SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID IN (SELECT * FROM CTE) AND PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' )

SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID,A.PRODUCT_NAME FROM (SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID,P.PRODUCT_NAME,MIN(S.SALE_DATE) MIN_DATE,MAX(S.SALE_DATE) MAX_DATE FROM SALES S JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID=P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID) A WHERE A.MIN_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND A.MAX_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31'

SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID=P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE>='2019-01-01' AND S.SALE_DATE<='2019-03-31' AND P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE>'2019-03-31'OR SALE_DATE<'2019-01-01')
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(S.SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31' AND MIN(S.SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01'

SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT LEFT JOIN SALES ON PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID = SALES.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= CAST('2019-01-01' AS DATE) AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= CAST('2019-03-31' AS DATE)

WITH TEMP_TABLE AS ( SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME, S.SALE_DATE FROM PRODUCT AS P INNER JOIN SALES AS S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID ) SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM TEMP_TABLE WHERE SALE_DATE >= '2019-01-01' AND SALE_DATE <= '2019-03-31' AND PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM TEMP_TABLE WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' )
SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S JOIN PRODUCT P USING(PRODUCT_ID) GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING SUM(IF(S.SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31', 1, 0)) = 0
SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT HAVING PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN DATE('2019-01-01') AND DATE('2019-03-31'))
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P LEFT JOIN SALES S ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(S.SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(S.SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'
SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID IN( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31')

WITH SELL_HISTORY AS ( SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, SUM(CASE WHEN SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) SOLD_OUTSIDE, SUM(CASE WHEN SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) SOLD_INSIDE FROM SALES S GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID ) SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SELL_HISTORY S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SOLD_OUTSIDE = 0 AND S.SOLD_INSIDE > 0

SELECT DISTINCT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P INNER JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID=S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND S.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT(PRODUCT_ID) FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31')
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID=S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY 1 HAVING MIN(S.SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(S.SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT AS P WHERE P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES AS S WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' )

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID , P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P WHERE '2019-01-01'<=(SELECT MIN(S.SALE_DATE) FROM SALES S WHERE S.PRODUCT_ID=P.PRODUCT_ID) AND '2019-03-31'>=(SELECT MAX(S.SALE_DATE) FROM SALES S WHERE S.PRODUCT_ID=P.PRODUCT_ID)
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P WHERE P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN( SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES A WHERE A.SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR A.SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31')

SELECT DISTINCT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S INNER JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND S.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE (SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31'))

SELECT DISTINCT(P.PRODUCT_ID),P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID=S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31')

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT DISTINCT A.PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCT A LEFT JOIN SALES B ON A.PRODUCT_ID = B.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' ) SELECT DISTINCT A.PRODUCT_ID, A.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT A LEFT JOIN SALES B ON A.PRODUCT_ID = B.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE >= '2019-01-01' AND SALE_DATE <= '2019-03-31' AND A.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM TEMP)
SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES AS S JOIN PRODUCT AS P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'
SELECT SALES.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES JOIN PRODUCT ON SALES.PRODUCT_ID = PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY SALES.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >='2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE)<='2019-03-31'
SELECT A1.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT AS A1 JOIN SALES AS A2 USING(PRODUCT_ID) GROUP BY 1 HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE)>='2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE)<='2019-03-31'
SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID,PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID=S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

SELECT DISTINCT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-04-01' ) ORDER BY 1

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID , PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P INNER JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(S.SALE_DATE)>='2019-01-01' AND MAX(S.SALE_DATE)<='2019-03-31'

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P WHERE (P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME) NOT IN ( SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31')

SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES JOIN PRODUCT ON SALES.PRODUCT_ID = PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALES.SALE_DATE) BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND MAX(SALES.SALE_DATE) BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31'

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT AS P INNER JOIN SALES AS S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME HAVING '2019-01-01' <= MIN(S.SALE_DATE) AND MAX(S.SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

SELECT DISTINCT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE (SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') AND PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID)
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P WHERE P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN( SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES S WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' )
SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID)

SELECT P.PRODUCT_NAME, S.PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES S JOIN PRODUCT P ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01'AND '2019-03-31' AND S.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01'AND '2019-03-31') GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID ORDER BY S.PRODUCT_ID

WITH IN_RANGE AS ( SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT INNER JOIN SALES ON SALES.PRODUCT_ID = PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALES.SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' ), OUT_RANGE AS ( SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT INNER JOIN SALES ON SALES.PRODUCT_ID = PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALES.SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' ) SELECT * FROM IN_RANGE WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM OUT_RANGE )
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(S.SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(S.SALE_DATE) < '2019-03-31'

SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT AS P LEFT JOIN SALES AS S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= CAST('2019-01-01' AS DATE) AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= CAST('2019-03-31' AS DATE)
SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' OR SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01')

SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID,P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(SALE_DATE)<='2019-03-31' AND MIN(SALE_DATE)>='2019-01-01')S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID=P.PRODUCT_ID

WITH SPRING AS( SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' ) SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID,S.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SPRING S LEFT JOIN (SELECT * FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31')A ON S.PRODUCT_ID = A.PRODUCT_ID WHERE A.PRODUCT_ID IS NULL

SELECT DISTINCT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P LEFT JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31')

WITH PRODUCT_SALE AS ( SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE>'2019-03-31' OR SALE_DATE<'2019-01-01' ) SELECT DISTINCT SALES.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES LEFT JOIN PRODUCT ON SALES.PRODUCT_ID = PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALES.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT * FROM PRODUCT_SALE)
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P LEFT JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE)>='2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE)<= '2019-03-31'
FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' )

SELECT T.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' ) ) AS T ON T.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY 1, 2 HAVING MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31' AND MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01'

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P WHERE (DATEDIFF((SELECT MIN(S.SALE_DATE) FROM SALES S WHERE S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID), '2019-01-01') >= 0) AND (DATEDIFF((SELECT MAX(S.SALE_DATE) FROM SALES S WHERE S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID), '2019-03-31') <= 0)

WITH C1 AS ( SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' ) SELECT DISTINCT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' )

SELECT A1.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME FROM (SELECT DISTINCT SALES.PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALES.SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND SALES.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT SALES.PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALES.SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31')) A1 JOIN PRODUCT ON A1.PRODUCT_ID = PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID ORDER BY A1.PRODUCT_ID

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALES.SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALES.SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' )
SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P WHERE P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT(PRODUCT_ID) FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31')

SELECT DISTINCT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES AS S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT AS P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31')
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID,P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT AS P JOIN SALES AS S ON P.PRODUCT_ID=S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(SALE_DATE)<= '2019-03-31' AND MIN(SALE_DATE)>='2019-01-01'

SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCT JOIN SALES ON PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID = SALES.PRODUCT_ID AND (SALES.SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALES.SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31') )

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN ( SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES S INNER JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31')

SELECT DISTINCT A.PRODUCT_ID,A.PRODUCT_NAME FROM (SELECT SALES.PRODUCT_ID, SALES.SALE_DATE, PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES JOIN PRODUCT ON SALES.PRODUCT_ID=PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID)AS A WHERE A.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE<'2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE>'2019-03-31')

SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S INNER JOIN PRODUCT P ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE > '2018-12-31' AND SALE_DATE <= '2019-03-31' AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM SALES S2 WHERE S2.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID AND (S2.SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR S2.SALE_DATE >'2019-03-31')) GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT AS P INNER JOIN SALES AS S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME HAVING MIN(IF(SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31',1, 0)) = 1

SELECT DISTINCT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31')

SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID,P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID=S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID=S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE>'2019-03-31' OR S.SALE_DATE<'2019-01-01' ) ORDER BY P.PRODUCT_ID

SELECT B.PRODUCT_ID, A.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES AS B JOIN PRODUCT AS A ON B.PRODUCT_ID=A.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY B.PRODUCT_ID,A.PRODUCT_NAME HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE)>='2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE)<='2019-03-31'

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID FROM PRODUCT P LEFT JOIN SALES S ON S.PRODUCT_ID=P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR S.SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31')
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT AS P WHERE P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31')

WITH EXCLUDE AS(SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID,P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID=S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID,P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P WHERE P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN(SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM EXCLUDE)
SELECT PRODUCT_ID, MAX(PRODUCT_NAME) PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT RIGHT JOIN SALES USING(PRODUCT_ID) GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(QUARTER(SALE_DATE)) = 1
SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= ('2019-01-01') AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= ('2019-03-31')

SELECT PRODUCT_ID,PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID IN (SELECT DISTINCT(PRODUCT_ID) FROM SALES WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE<'2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE>'2019-03-31'))

SELECT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_ID IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING (MAX(SALE_DATE) BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') AND (MIN(SALE_DATE) BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31'))

SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S LEFT JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID=P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-04-1' AND S.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE <='2018-12-31') AND S.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE >='2019-4-1') GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID

SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID, (SELECT PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID=SALES.PRODUCT_ID) AS PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE >= '2019-01-01' AND SALE_DATE <= '2019-03-31' AND PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31')

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID,P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT AS P RIGHT JOIN SALES AS S ON S.PRODUCT_ID=P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND S.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN(SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID) GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID

(SELECT DISTINCT(SALE.PRODUCT_ID), PROD.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES SALE, PRODUCT PROD WHERE (SALE.PRODUCT_ID = PROD.PRODUCT_ID) AND SALE.SALE_DATE >= '2019-01-01' AND SALE.SALE_DATE<='2019-03-31' AND SALE.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT SALE.PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES SALE, PRODUCT PROD WHERE SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01' OR SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31') ) ORDER BY SALE.PRODUCT_ID ASC

SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S INNER JOIN PRODUCT P ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

WITH TEMP_TABLE AS (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES S WHERE (S.SALE_DATE >= '2019-01-01' AND S.SALE_DATE <= '2019-03-31') AND S.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' OR SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01')) SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID,P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM TEMP_TABLE T JOIN PRODUCT P ON T.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID ORDER BY T.PRODUCT_ID

SELECT DISTINCT PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES JOIN PRODUCT USING (PRODUCT_ID) WHERE PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN'2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') AND PRODUCT_ID IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE BETWEEN'2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31')

SELECT P1.PRODUCT_ID, P1.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P1 JOIN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID, MIN(SALE_DATE) AS MIN_DATE, MAX(SALE_DATE) AS MAX_DATE FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID) AS P2 ON P1.PRODUCT_ID = P2.PRODUCT_ID AND P2.MIN_DATE >= DATE('2019-01-01') AND P2.MAX_DATE <= DATE('2019-03-31')
SELECT P1.PRODUCT_ID,P1.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P1 JOIN SALES S1 ON P1.PRODUCT_ID=S1.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY P1.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MAX(QUARTER(SALE_DATE ))=1

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P JOIN SALES S ON S.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE P.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID

SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_ID,PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P INNER JOIN SALES S ON P.PRODUCT_ID=S.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM PRODUCT PP INNER JOIN SALES SS ON PP.PRODUCT_ID=SS.PRODUCT_ID WHERE SS.SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' AND P.PRODUCT_ID=PP.PRODUCT_ID)

SELECT SALES.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES RIGHT JOIN PRODUCT ON PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID= SALES.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY SALES.PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

SELECT S.PRODUCT_ID ,P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM SALES S INNER JOIN PRODUCT P ON P.PRODUCT_ID = S.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID ,P.PRODUCT_NAME HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31'

SELECT A.PRODUCT_ID, A.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT A WHERE A.PRODUCT_ID IN ( SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING (MAX(SALE_DATE) <= STR_TO_DATE('2019-03-31','%Y-%M-%D')) AND (MIN(SALE_DATE) >= STR_TO_DATE('2019-01-01','%Y-%M-%D')) )

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT P INNER JOIN (SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING MIN(SALE_DATE) >= '2019-01-01' AND MAX(SALE_DATE) <= '2019-03-31') SPRINGPRODUCTS ON SPRINGPRODUCTS.PRODUCT_ID = P.PRODUCT_ID

SELECT P.PRODUCT_ID,P.PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT AS P RIGHT JOIN SALES AS S ON S.PRODUCT_ID=P.PRODUCT_ID WHERE S.PRODUCT_ID NOT IN(SELECT PRODUCT_ID FROM SALES WHERE SALE_DATE NOT BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID) AND S.SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31' GROUP BY S.PRODUCT_ID

SELECT PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID, PRODUCT_NAME FROM PRODUCT JOIN SALES ON PRODUCT.PRODUCT_ID = SALES.PRODUCT_ID GROUP BY PRODUCT_ID HAVING SUM(SALE_DATE BETWEEN '2019-01-01' AND '2019-03-31') > 0 AND SUM(SALE_DATE > '2019-03-31' OR SALE_DATE < '2019-01-01') = 0
